, expired documents, eligibility, ATT or rejections caused by applicants' failure to check their emails.</u></b> Applicant must inform NEAC if there is any change in their contact information and email address. <u>However, it is still applicants’ responsibility to contact NEAC to follow up their applications if not heard from NEAC more than a month.</u><br><br>
